<section xml:id="week1-activity">
  <title>Week 1 Activity</title>
  <subsection xml:id="problems-vectors">
    <title>Vector Arithmetic</title>
    <activity>
      <statement>
        <p>
          For the vectors <m>u = (4,5)</m> and <m>v = (-1, -3)</m>,
          calculate operations. Draw the first three.
        </p>
        <p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <me>
                u + v = (4+(-1)1, 5+(-3)) = (3,2) 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                u - v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                \frac{1}{4} u - \frac{3}{5} v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>  
                |u|
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                |u - v| 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>  
                u \cdot v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              The angle between <m>u</m> and <m>v</m>. 
            </li>
          </ol>
        </p>
      </statement>
      <solution>
        <p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <me>
                u + v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                u - v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                \frac{1}{4} u - \frac{3}{5} v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>  
                |u|
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>
                |u - v| 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              <me>  
                u \cdot v 
              </me>
            </li>
            <li>
              The angle between <m>u</m> and <m>v</m> is calculated
              via the dot product
              <me>
                \theta = \arccos \left( \frac{u \cdot v}{|u||v|} 
              </me>
            </li>
          </ol>
          Here is the diagram of the first three calculations.
          <figure xml:id="figure-vector-activities1">
            <caption>Vector Operatiors Activity 1</caption>
            <image xml:id="image-vector-activities1">
              <asymptote>
                size(10cm);
                import graph;

                xlimits(0,5);
                ylimits(0,5);

                xaxis("$x$",Ticks("%"));
                yaxis("$y$",Ticks("%"));

                draw((0,0)--(1,2),Arrow); 

                label("$u = (1,2)$, (1,2),E);
              </asymptote>
            </image>
          </figure>
        </p>
      </solution>
    </activity>
